We are looking for a middle QA Engineer (part-time or full-time) to join our team. We are a top-rated plus e-commerce web development company Polyany s.r.o. (located in the EU, Czech Republic / Ukraine, and founded in 2017).
The ideal candidate should have at least 3 years in manual web solutions testing, including Prestashop, Shopify e-commerce sites, applications, etc.
Requirements of hard skills for a QA specialist:
- great manual testing knowledge of websites, web applications, and API integration;
- good knowledge of e-commerce Shopify, Prestashop, or Magento platforms;
- basic knowledge of web technologies (HTML5/CSS3, Liquid, JS and PHP);
- good knowledge of tools for test management and bug tracking;
- at least B1 English level (intermediate)
Requirements of soft skills for a QA specialist:
- attention to detail, problem-solving skills, critical thinking, and analytical skills;
- time management and punctuality in following project agreements (quality, scope, and deadlines);
- good communication skills and empathy;
- flexibility and teamwork
Responsibilities of a QA engineer: - analyze and clarification of requirements with a customer or a project manager;
- plan the process of testing;
- write test cases; - conduct functional testing;
- identify problem areas, and add them to a tracking system;
- discuss fixes with developers;
- re-test fixed defects;
- analyze testing; - optimize the testing process;
- maintain the test documentation
We will be glad to offer interesting web projects of custom B2C or B2B e-commerce solutions and great working conditions with our progressive team.
We will be glad to talk with you in more detail!

